criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Body mass index between 18.5 and 24.9 kg/m² or equal or greater 35 kg/m²;

          -  Able to sign the informed consent.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Chronic health conditions (e.g. chronic renal failure, autoimmune, heart, and, liver
             disease);

          -  Thyroid diseases or medications for its treatment;

          -  Medications known to affect total energy expenditure;

          -  Use of steroids, immunosuppressants, or non-steroidal anti-inflammatory drugs,
             weight-loss medications, oral hypoglycemic agents or insulin, and any medications that
             influence metabolic and/or inflammatory parameters;

          -  Previous surgery for weight loss;

          -  Pregnancy and breast-feeding;

          -  Smoking;

          -  Alcohol use (>2 doses/day).
